title: You Have No Problems
itunes:title: You Have No Problems
description:
Episode 139 - Problems do not exist in reality, the only exist in our minds. There are no real problems, there are only challenges and we decided whether or not we want to conquer them. In this episode I dive deep into problems and how we view them in our minds so that we can overcome them in reality.
